            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Deo Soli <expan><abbr>Alagabal</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> <note>sic</note> <lb n="2"/>Ammudati <expan><abbr>mil</abbr><ex>ites</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> I <expan><abbr>ad</abbr><ex>iutricis</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>bis <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>iae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>idelis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Cons</abbr><ex>tantis</ex></expan> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <lb n="0"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/><certainty match="preceding-sibling::node()" locus="value"/>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Gefunden beim Bau der Kirche; jetzt verschollen. Wohl kaum zugehörig sind die überlieferten Zeilen 4-6: aere conl(ato) a solo de suo / temp(lum) ex(s)tr(uxerunt) Aemiliano / et Aquil(ino) co(n)s(ulibus).</p>
            </div>
